sightings.title: Toucan Paradise
sightings.description: Visited an area filled with toucans of various species. Their vibrant beaks and playful behavior were a delight to observe.

sightings.title: Jaguar Sighting
sightings.description: Had a rare sighting of a jaguar roaming in its natural habitat. Stayed still to admire this magnificent creature from afar.

sightings.title: Majestic Tiger Sighting
sightings.description: Spotted a beautiful tiger near the riverbank during my jungle expedition. It was a breathtaking sight!
